740
00:33:43.960 --> 00:33:45.310
<font color="#ffff00">Denn eine stabile Altersvorsorge</font>
<font color="#ffff00">ist wichtig.</font>

741
00:33:46.130 --> 00:33:48.110
<font color="#ffff00">Aber was es kostet,</font>
